Description:
I am an Audio Engineerspecialized in telling stories through sound. I will work closely with you to take your project to the next level: add more excitement, impact, drama, atmosphere and complete immersion. All done with professional and industry-standard tools, optimized for today's main streaming services.

**Feel free to contact me if you need:**

* Sound Design
* Dialogue Editing and Restoration
* Mixing and Mastering

**All packages include Sound Design, Dialogue Editing, Mixing, and Mastering.**

I can deliver in stems and with a 2-pop for better sync with your editor.

**I create:**

* Short documentaries and/or vlogs;
* Trailers;
* Advertisements;
* Corporate videos;
* Podcasts and podcast intros;
* Sound branding;
* Intros for Youtube videos.

**Make sure to contact me first and tell me what you have in mind. Feel free to send me reference videos that you'd like to be inspired by.**

**Got questions? Have a big project that could use my work? Feel free to contact me anytime and I'll be glad to help you!**

**Please make sure to reach out before placing an order to confirm my availability and discuss timelines, as some projects may need extended deadlines regardless of their duration.**
